description:
We start the workshop with something very fun and exiting and icebreaking :-) You will meet similar minded singles and be able to learn about them and apply what you have learned to see if any of the singles attending could be a match for you:-)

We cover several topics including the value of your decisions in finding your partner, the value of your 'filters' in stopping you from seeing your partner and the points which could be the 'deal maker' or 'deal breakers'. The workshop is delivered with simple but super powerful and workable methods which you practice during the workshop. 

The workshop will be around 2.5-3 hours (depending on nr. of attendees).

There is a minimum fee of euro 20 per attendee which covers the logistics.

Register for the seminar and take your next step toward learning and applying simple workable tools to get your to your ideal partner :-)

Please ensure you submit your mobile and email on the reservation so I can contact you in case of any changes. 

To you future success in a stable, loving and caring relationship :-)
name: Workshop for Singles

description:
During this Fun Workshop you will meet other singles, hear about the viewpoints and understandings of the "other sex", while at the same time, You will find answers to the following questions:'

Are there different types of LOVE?

What are the foundations of a real stable relationship?

Why do you 'Doubt' the possibility for having a stable loving relationship?

Are you actually mentally 'AVAILABLE' for a relationship?rs

What are some  of the most important factors which can make or break a relationship?

You will also get some tips and do some exercises on:

How to start a conversation with another...

How to open-up yourself....

How to understand yourself a bit better....

How to become better in a relationship....

And many more .....


The workshop starts with an icebreaking game which is liked by many, creating an atmosphere of friendliness and comfort. 

Register for the Workshop and start your journey to finding your Ideal Partner :-)

While having FUN :-)

description:
Did you ever Roller-Coaster in your emotions? One day up.... the next day feeling down?

When you feel happy, and for no apparent reason, suddenly start feeling down, somebody made this happen.

Attend the workshop and get the basic fundamental reasons why you go up and down in humor.

The workshop gives opportunity to understand the basic fundamentals and possibility to do some practical exercises.

There is a minimum fee of 30 Euros per attendees.

Only RSVP with valid email and mobile number will be considered valid.
